No one wants to ban our cakes.
Vicen also addressed the agenda that the European Council lived, lives and will live in the near future.
The Czech Presidency was a success.
The Czechs addressed the emerging financial crisis, resolved the gas crisis, or held a summit for the Eastern Partnership.
She described the fall of the government at this time as a great negativum, which severely damaged the Czech Republic.
The Czech delegation in the EU is currently very busy.
Speaking in the words of the ambassador, "fakt frmol" was not only the presidency, but also the subsequent financial crisis, which is addressed to this day.
